<br>
Garions issue is that he's a high level Druid trying to solo with Nature spec.  Sorry, solo'ing past 35 for a Druid slows down dramtically.  Am I sad for Druids?  Not really, this is a group game in the long run (the R in RvR doesn't mean Mano on Mano), and a Nurture first, Regrowth second Druid is where the money's at, as long as they can stay alive to keep those buffs up on our Heros they're worth their weight in Mithril.<br>
<br>
Giving pets to Druids to maximize their soloability was the single most stupid class deisgn mistake made by Mythic, coming in a close second is the overall setup for a Mentalist.<br>
<br>
The Archer 'nerf' was primarly for RvR.  Any depowering of the Archers in RvR has a serious side effect of their ability to play in PvE.  To be honest, I deem any Ranger/Nightshade to be just an XP leech, as much as an Eldritch.  Will I level them up for the good of the realm?  Yes.  But do I want more then 2 of them in any 1 group?  No.<br>
