I just can't seem to understand Mythic's stance on archery right now. It seems like it's repeatedly being nerfed (since beta), and at the rate it's going they're going to render &quot;pure&quot; archers inviable. There's already several classes that have the capability to completely negate the archer's bread and butter attack (crit), and tanks using abilities like engage give you such a low chance to hit, it's a better idea to run away and pick a different (softer) target. People seem to overlook the fact that archers only get a couple shots, and if that doesn't work, their best bet is to run like hell and hide (at least in a RvR environment... they won't survive melee against a tank unless they did HEAVY damage beforehand).<br>
<br>
